summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the land use and zoning; amending Plat 29E, Page 90 for the Official Land Use Map to rezone certain property located on both sides of Eighth Avenue North between Hays and Garfield Streets from Manufacturing (M) Zone to Community Business (CB) Zone. (Petition of Russell "Buzz" Keyes, R.K. Investments; C.F. No. 291758).
